full_title: Made For Me by Muni Long
title: Made For Me

description.plain:
“Made For Me” is a piano-led, R&B ballad, serving as the lead single from her fourth studio album (and seventh release overall), Revenge.

It became Muni Long’s second hit to reach the top 20 on the US Billboard Hot 100, achieving platinum status from the RIAA in May 2024. It also remains her biggest hit in the UK and Canada. This is mainly owed to its TikTok virality in January 2024, which caused the song to surge on social media and streaming platforms.
